<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FlowTask - O Futuro da Gestão Empresarial</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary: #8b5cf6;
            --primary-dark: #7c3aed;
            --secondary: #06b6d4;
            --accent: #f59e0b;
            --success: #10b981;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --dark: #0f0f23;
            --dark-lighter: #1a1a2e;
            --dark-card: #16213e;
            --text-primary: #e2e8f0;
            --text-secondary: #94a3b8;
            --gradient-main: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            --gradient-purple: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
            --gradient-blue: linear-gradient(135deg, #06b6d4 0%, #0891b2 100%);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: var(--dark);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* Animated background */
        .bg-animation {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%),
                        radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .bg-animation::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="rgba(139,92,246,0.1)" stroke-width="0.5"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100" height="100" fill="url(%23grid)" /></svg>');
            animation: float 90s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
            33% { transform: translate(30px, -30px) rotate(120deg); }
            66% { transform: translate(-20px, 20px) rotate(240deg); }
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        header.scrolled {
            background: rgba(15, 15, 35, 0.95);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        }

        nav {
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 1.6rem;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--gradient-main);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        .logo::before {
            content: '🧠';
            font-size: 1.44rem;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 1.6rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.6rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 3.2px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            font-size: 0.96rem;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            min-height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 1.6rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3.2rem;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-text h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

        .hero-text .highlight {
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero-text p {
            font-size: 1.04rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 3.2px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            color: var(--primary);
            border: 1.6px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Hero Visual */
        .hero-visual {
            position: relative;
            height: 480px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .dashboard-preview {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(5deg);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .dashboard-preview:hover {
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-2deg) rotateX(2deg) scale(1.02);
        }

        .dashboard-header {
            background: var(--dark-lighter);
            padding: 0.8rem;
            border-bottom: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .dashboard-header::before {
            content: '';
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            background: #ef4444;
            border-radius: 50%;
            box-shadow: 16px 0 #f59e0b, 32px 0 #10b981;
        }

        .dashboard-header .dashboard-title {
            margin-left: 30px;
        }

        .dashboard-content {
            padding: 1.6rem;
            height: calc(100% - 64px);
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            border-radius: 9.6px;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            border: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .card-icon {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.96rem;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .card-value {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        /* Features Section */
        .features {
            padding: 6.4rem 1.6rem;
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }

        .section-header h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.4rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .section-header p {
            font-size: 0.96rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.6rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: rgba(16, 33, 62, 0.5);
            border: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .feature-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-card:hover::before {
            transform: scaleX(1);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.12rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .feature-list li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
        }

        .feature-list li::before {
            content: '✓';
            color: var(--success);
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 16px;
        }

        /* Stats Section */
        .stats {
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            padding: 4.8rem 1.6rem;
            margin: 3.2rem 0;
            border-top: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            border-bottom: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        }

        .stats-container {
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.4rem;
            margin-top: 2.4rem;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Pricing Section */
        .pricing {
            padding: 6.4rem 1.6rem;
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(256px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.6rem;
            margin-top: 2.4rem;
        }

        .pricing-card {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            border: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .pricing-card.featured {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
        }

        .pricing-card.featured::before {
            content: 'MAIS POPULAR';
            position: absolute;
            top: -9.6px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-size: 0.64rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .pricing-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }

        .pricing-card.featured:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-10px);
        }

        .pricing-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .price {
            font-size: 2.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        .price-period {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
        }

        .pricing-features {
            list-style: none;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .pricing-features li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            font-size: 0.72rem;
        }

        .pricing-features li::before {
            content: '✓';
            color: var(--success);
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 16px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: var(--dark-lighter);
            padding: 3.2rem 1.6rem 1.6rem;
            border-top: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
        }

        .footer-content {
            max-width: 1120px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
        }

        .footer-section h3 {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .footer-section p {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .footer-section ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .footer-section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-section ul li a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 1.6rem;
            border-top: 0.8px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes slideInRight {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(50px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .animate-on-scroll {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: all 0.6s ease;
        }

        .animate-on-scroll.animated {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Mobile Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .card-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
.card-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.96rem;
        }
            .card-value {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: var(--gradient-purple);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

            .hero-visual {
            position: relative;
            height: auto; /* Let it grow with content */
            min-height: 220px; /* Optional: ensures it's not too small */
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .lead-form-section {
            padding: 1.5rem 0.5rem;
            margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08);
            max-width: 100%;
        }
        .lead-form {
            gap: 0.7rem;
            max-width: 100%;
        }
        .lead-form .form-row {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        .lead-form input,
        .lead-form textarea {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 1rem 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            min-width: 0;
        }
        .lead-form button[type="submit"] {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .success-message,
        .error-message {
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 0.5rem 0.2rem;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
            .hero-text h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1.1;
        }

            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 1.6rem;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .hero-visual {
                height: 320px;
            }

            .dashboard-preview {
                transform: none;
            }

            .hero-buttons {
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .stats-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 1.6rem;
            }

            .pricing-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .pricing-card.featured {
                transform: none;
            }
        }

        /* Floating Elements */
        .floating-element {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0.1;
            animation: floating 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .floating-element:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
        .floating-element:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 2s; }
        .floating-element:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 4s; }

        @keyframes floating {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-animation"></div>

    <header id="header">
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">FlowTask</div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#features">Funcionalidades</a></li>
                <li><a href="#pricing">Preços</a></li>
                <li><a href="#lead-form">Contacto</a></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="#lead-form" class="cta-button">Começar Grátis</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1>
                    O Futuro da <span class="highlight">Gestão Empresarial</span> com Inteligência Artificial
                </h1>
                <p>
                    Revolucione a sua produtividade com a plataforma mais avançada para gestão de clientes, tarefas, tempos e obrigações fiscais. Powered by AI.
                </p>
                <div class="hero-buttons">
                    <a href="#lead-form" class="btn-primary">
                        🚀 Teste Grátis 30 Dias
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-visual">
                <div class="dashboard-preview">
                    <div class="dashboard-header">
                        <span class="dashboard-title">FlowTask Dashboard</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="dashboard-content">
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
                                <div class="card-title">Receita Total</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-value">€1,530</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
                                <div class="card-title">Tarefas Ativas</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-value">6</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-header">
                                <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
                                <div class="card-title">Rentabilidade</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-value">69.5%</div>
                        </div>
